## Questions to Ask Before Proceeding

When in doubt, Claude should ask:
1. "Should this be a new dependency or can we use existing tools?"
2. "Does this change require a database migration?"
3. "Should this be a server component or client component?"
4. "Where does this fit in the existing folder structure?"
5. "Does this need tests?" (always yes for [critical paths])

